# Specials Rules
## Combat Formations
***
### Line Formation
* Leader must be in first line of the formation
* All units of the formation must be in base contact so as to form a rectangle.
* The formation can't runnig, otherwise the formation is broken
* When a squad or a platoon is in formation, all units of the formation can move 3 ps at the beggining of each phase to reform. (The leader can't move)
* For **Line Infantry** and **Elite infantry**
***
### Square Formation
* Leader must be in middle of the formation
* All units of the formation must be in base contact so as to form a square.
* The formation can't runnig, otherwise the formation is broken
* When a squad or a platoon is in formation, all units of the formation can move 3 ps at the beggining of each phase to reform. (The leader can't move)
* For **Line Infantry** and **Elite infantry**

## Orders
* **En joue ! Feu !** : All units can have _precision shots_
  * Must be in **Line Formation** or in **Square Formation**
* **Fire at will !** : The units can shoot on two targets
  * Must be in **Line Formation** or in **Square Formation**
* **First Rank, Fire ! Second Rank Fire !** : All lasguns fire add 1 shot
  * Must be in **Line Formation** or in **Square Formation**
* **Go !! For the emperor !** : The unit MUST shoot AND sprint in the same turn. The formation is broken 
  * Must be in **Line Formation**
* **Go !! Go !! Go !!** : The unit MUST sprint. Roll 3 dices and keep the Higher. The formation is broken 
  * Must be in **Line Formation**
* **Supress Fire !** : All weapons have _pinning_ special rule
  * Must be in **Line Formation** or in **Square Formation**

* **Kill Him !!** (_High Officers_ only) : All units have _armourbane_ and _monster hunter_ special rule
  * Must be in **Line Formation** or in **Square Formation**
* **Target Acquired !** (_High Officers_ only) : All weapons have _ignore covers_ special rule
  * Must be in **Line Formation** or in **Square Formation**
* **Get back in fight !** (_High Officers_ only) : Only for units in _retreat_ or _to ground !_. All effects cease immediatly and the unit can act normaly
